                     <interp inst="t17770219-14-person205" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             came there under suspicious circumstances; I pulled him off his horse, and found a pair of loaded pistols upon him.</p>
               <p>
                  <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="177702190033"></xptr>
            
                  <persName id="t17770219-14-person206">
                  JOSEPH
                   WILSON
